{"_id":"ATZpc9fGgK1rjg9f","name":"Statue - Dwarf King","permission":{"default":0,"ZjdmMWEyMmE2NzVk":3},"folder":"PcxysbWCxMCHKEgn","sort":200000,"flags":{},"content":"<p>The statue is life-size and depicts a dwarf king standing atop a 3-foot-high stone pedestal. Sprouting from the king's neck is a deformed, mostly featureless second head with an elongated, toothless mouth. The inscriptions on the pedestal have been worn away. On the king's brow rests an engraved stone circlet, and his large hands grasp the handle of a stone warhammer, the head of which is planted at his feet.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>Halaster used stone shape spells to create the statue's second head and rub away the inscriptions on the pedestal. Even the Mad Mage is unaware, however, that the statue hides a secret. Any character who examines the statue and succeeds on a DC 15 Wisdom (Perception) check notices that the king's warhammer is a separate piece of stone that can be rotated. When the warhammer is turned so that the weapon's backside faces forward, the pedestal rises another 3 feet, revealing an open cavity that contains a magic circlet identical to the one worn by the statue&mdash;but fashioned from gold rather than stone.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Treasure. The gold circlet is a circlet of blasting.</p>\n</section>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}
{"name":"App. A: Magic Items","permission":{"default":-1,"ZjdmMWEyMmE2NzVk":3},"folder":"xU2zPB5VIEAHK3ql","sort":1200001,"flags":{},"content":"<div class=\"w-100 overflow-x-hidden\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"1424\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Magic Items</span></span> <p>This appendix describes new magic items that appear in the adventure, and which are presented here in alphabetical order.</p><p>Several of these items are found in the possession of specific NPCs:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">Aurinax has the {<a href=\"https://5e.tools/items.html#dragonstaff%20of%20ahghairon_wdh\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'items.html', 'wdh', 'dragonstaff%20of%20ahghairon_wdh', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >dragonstaff of Ahghairon</a>}.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Jalester Silvermane has a {<a href=\"https://5e.tools/items.html#badge%20of%20the%20watch_wdh\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'items.html', 'wdh', 'badge%20of%20the%20watch_wdh', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >badge of the Watch</a>}.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Jarlaxle Baenre has a {<a href=\"https://5e.tools/items.html#bracer%20of%20flying%20daggers_wdh\"  onmouseover=\"Renderer.hover.pHandleLinkMouseOver(event, this, 'items.html', 'wdh', 'bracer%20of%20flying%20daggers_wdh', null)\" onmouseleave=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseLeave(event, this)\" onmousemove=\"Renderer.hover.handleLinkMouseMove(event, this)\"  ontouchstart=\"Renderer.hover.handleTouchStart(event, this)\" >bracer of flying daggers</a>}, a {<a href=\"https://5e.tool