{"_id":"N2UzOGI5MDk0Y2Nh","name":"+1 Breastplate","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZDVkNGI3NGVkMTk0","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":0,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":0,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>+1 Breastplate<br></h4><p><i>Armor (medium), rare</i><br></p><p>You have a +1 bonus to AC while wearing this armor. Manufactured by drow, this +1 breastplate loses its enhancement bonus if exposed to sunlight for 1 hour or more. Further examination of the drow also yields an obsidian scarab bearing the insignia of House Freth (25 gp).<br></p>\n<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><p><br></p></section>","img":""}
