{"_id":"NTE5MzJhNjA4YTFj","name":"Rollable Tokens","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ODAwNDU4MjE1ODdh","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":6,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":60000,"entryTime":0,"content":"\n<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><p>The tokens for <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=NDBhNjM1MjRjNGQx ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Arcanaloth</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=MmIzMzMzOWJlYWUx ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Archmage</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=OTcxYjFhZTZiNDZm ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Arcturia</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=YWQ0NTAwMTE4NjAz ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Assassin</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=NmQ2MjZlOGU4MWIw ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Bandit</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=NjZiZjVhOGQ0ZWZh ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Death Slaad</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=Y2Q1ZWRiYzA0MWVh ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Doppelganger</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=Zjc3ZWMwMzI5Nzg3 ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Drow Priestess of Lolth</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=ZWU1YmI3MjViZDQ3 ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Glyster</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=YzA2YzdhYTY3Y2Uw ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Goblin Boss</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=NjkyZTg5YmYxMTMx ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Gray Slaad</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=YWUxZmU4MmZlYTQx ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Green Slaad</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=MTJmNDE5OTUxY2M0 ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Halaster Blackcloak</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=NGIyMDEyMDAzMjM1 ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Incubus</a>, <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=ZTBkNmIyZDIxNDQ0 ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Keresta Delvingst