{"_id":"NjA2NmI0OTg4MzM5","name":"-Death Tyrant","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MDU0YWU4MzFmMTE1","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":6,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":60000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h1>Death Tyrant</h1><p>The Mad Mage has transformed an entire level of Undermountain into a proving ground for adventurers who seek to reach the deepest layers of the dungeon and the treasures hidden within. At the end of this underground obstacle course waits the greatest challenge of all: Netherskull the Death Tyrant, an undead beholder that hates wizards above all.</p><div><br></div>","img":"modules/dotmm-shared/journal/032_-_Secrets_Deck_Handouts/006_-_-Death_Tyrant/avatar.png"}
