{"_id":"YTJlMDUwNzhlMmMy","name":"Potion of Animal Friendship","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MzEwZWQwN2I5NTYw","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":1,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":10000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Potion of Animal Friendship</h4><p><i>Potion, uncommon</i><br></p><p>When you drink this potion, you can cast the <i><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Item data-id=Y2E4OWU2MjM4Yzcz ><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i>animal friendship</a></i> spell (save DC 13) for 1 hour at will. Agitating this muddy liquid brings little bits into view: a fish scale, a hummingbird tongue, a cat claw, or a squirrel hair.<br></p>\n<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><p><br></p></section>","img":""}
