{"_id":"ZTZiNzJlOGNjODM3","name":"Dagger of Venom","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZDVkNGI3NGVkMTk0","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":19,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":190000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Dagger of Venom<br></h4><p><i>Weapon (dagger), rare</i><br></p><p>You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.<br><br>You can use an action to cause thick, black poison to coat the blade. The poison remains for 1 minute or until an attack using this weapon hits a creature. That creature must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 2d10 poison damage and become poisoned for 1 minute. The dagger can't be used this way again until the next dawn.<br></p>","img":"modules/dotmm-shared/journal/029_-_Magic_Items/019_-_Dagger_of_Venom/avatar_1.png"}
